```
<%= %x(./joynd --help) %>
```

## Manpage
```
<%= %x(mandoc ./joynd.1 | col -b) %>
```

## Examples
Prior to sens9x-gtk I run the following script:
```
#!/bin/sh
joynd -d -i 0 \
        -b 7=q \
        -b 4=w \
        -b 5=e \
        -b 6=r \
        -b 13=t \
        -b 14=z \
        -b 15=u \
        -b 12=i \
        -b 3=o \
        -b 0=p \
        -b 10=a \
        -b 11=s
```

